      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GO GETTEM NELLY (2) was rewarded for her honesty after two minors on end with a deserved win last time, scoring at this track over 297m (17.13). The form out of her last race has been franked. The one to beat again. STARLIGHT TWIX (1) missed the frame last time, finishing 4th (17.65) last time in a Free For All at this track. Goes very well at course and distance boasting four wins. Cannot be taken lightly. POP DIVA (6) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 17.01 beating Bruiser My Uncle. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Can make it back-to-back wins. CHAROS NOBLE (8) scored last time and can measure up again.",
